name: .SELF File Extension
summary: Learn about .SELF files and view a list of programs that open them.

instructions: SELF files are not meant to be opened. The most common interaction gamers have with SELF files is installing them as part of the setup for RPCS3 (Windows, Linux), a PC-based PlayStation 3 emulator.
